{"tid":2312611,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"ITZY禮志深夜開直播被粉絲問：「妳不累嗎？ 」反應令人暖哭了！","createTime":"2020-12-05T06:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T15:16:47.000Z","uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"78aef4ec4cc1e4b2e0baaad6ac35bf2ef786cc47","tid":2312611,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T06:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_5e47d37082cbe60ea673f3c5ad698049/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-04/132105-887683.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_5e47d37082cbe60ea673f3c5ad698049%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-04%2F132105-887683.png&h=7dd5bf2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n誰不想聽到自家偶像講這樣的話呢？禮志看出粉絲擔心她「這麼晚還在工作」，溫柔地說：「我並不覺得和大家聊天是工作呀！」真的太甜了！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nITZY今年8月發行了迷你三輯《Not Shy》，近日在AAA頒獎禮斬獲「最佳選擇」和「HOT Issue」兩個獎項，作為出道不足2年的女團成績相當不錯！<br />\n<br />\n前幾天ITZY成員禮志第一次嘗試在深夜通過直播和大家聊天：「今天開始直播的時間確實有點晚呢，11點47分，第一次在這麼晚的時間開直播。 想著在這個時間問候一下MIDZY也不錯。 」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_5890722660dacc4237f0e77ba73353f8/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-04/132105-887675.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_5890722660dacc4237f0e77ba73353f8%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-04%2F132105-887675.png&h=94a46ac4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這時有粉絲擔心地留言問：「不會累嗎？ 」禮志馬上表示：「我是因為喜歡才開直播的呀，有什麼好累的呢？ 只是和MIDZY說話呀。 」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_3fb542ef3cd544b75f2b06adca6374f3/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-04/132105-887677.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_3fb542ef3cd544b75f2b06adca6374f3%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-04%2F132105-887677.png&h=43e90457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n禮志看了一下大家的留言突然反應過來：「好像MIDZY覺得V APP是工作的一部份。 MIDZY，我不這樣想的。 我想多多和MIDZY說話，經常說話，反倒是擔心MIDZY覺得我煩呢。 」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_bb28a77e9459b35874cd37f0149abeb1/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-04/132105-887679.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_bb28a77e9459b35874cd37f0149abeb1%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-04%2F132105-887679.png&h=d45cd57b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n禮志問：「我是不是太經常過來了呢？ 」很多人留言說：「沒有！沒問題的！」禮志笑著說：「我不會覺得麻煩哦！不會不會~」真的好暖~<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_25064e7f04001df1fda7812a230756bc/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-04/132105-887681.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_25064e7f04001df1fda7812a230756bc%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-04%2F132105-887681.png&h=b623b753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這時有粉絲開玩笑說「MIDZY可是有點忙呢」，也被禮志看到了，她笑著說：「MIDZY又在調皮耶！也有不調皮的MIDZY，不過總有幾個調皮的MIDZY。 那麼我暫且認為這是不錯的主意哦。！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_0137cfef62734793c977caebc21fc2fd/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-04/132105-887682.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_0137cfef62734793c977caebc21fc2fd%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-04%2F132105-887682.png&h=daa7fd38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n禮志在直播裡還給了MIDZY一個大大的擁抱，真的是一段讓人看了會忍不住嘴角上揚的影片！這次直播的完整重播可以點這裡收看~<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FjcpO_ajJIg&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFjcpO_ajJIg%26feature%3Demb_title&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w9ey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=b5554169\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FjcpO_ajJIg&amp;feature=emb_title</a>"},{"pid":"6d7474b8d38bf8e4124ee7c81747dd84aeb61ab6","tid":2312611,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T06:11:32.000Z","msg":"好好的女仔😳💘✊🏼"},{"pid":"043a8bba6d35d7ab1be8b7d2634e45b7462ecdb3","tid":2312611,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T06:11:43.000Z","msg":"今日很凍 攬住彩瑛同Mina取暖中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" 